metadata.title: Where can I find Application Projects for RA Family and FSP?

sections.content: Where can I find Application Projects for RA Family and FSP?
You can find example projects for RA devices and FSP in our official github repo here:
In application_projects folder you will find the sample code available of our Application Notes.
In example_projects folder you will find example projects for almost all the Evaluation Kits and Fast Prototyping Boards available.
